  p.slug microsoft regional directors 

  p#dimensions for debugging
  
  :markdown
    The Microsoft Regional Director program has a new logo. In keeping with the 
    spirit of Microsoft's 2012 corporate and product line rebranding, the <abbr>RD</abbr>
    logo was refashioned to reflect their new design asthetic:

    - Monochromatic
    - Segoe typeface
    - Simple layout and icon
    - Semantic HTML

  h2 The Logo
  p
    Three sizes of <abbr>PNG</abbr> images to choose from, with two variations:
    white background or transparent background.

  :markdown
    - Small: 336 x 96 pixels [white][1] [transparent][2]
    - Medium: 672 x 192 pixels [white][3] [transparent][4]
    - Large: 1344 x 384 pixels [white][5] [transparent][6]

    [1]: logo/msrd-logo-96px.png "small white"
    [2]: logo/msrd-logo-96px-alpha.png "small transparent"
    [3]: logo/msrd-logo-192px.png "small white"
    [4]: logo/msrd-logo-192px-alpha.png "small transparent"
    [5]: logo/msrd-logo-384px.png "small white"
    [6]: logo/msrd-logo-384px-alpha.png "small transparent"

